            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數上漲1141.9點至38856.05點，漲幅3.03%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間24日12:47，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1141.9點（或3.03%），暫報38856.05點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.57%</li><li>近 1 月：+15.25%</li><li>近 3 月：+18%</li><li>近 6 月：+36.98%</li><li>今年以來：+30.21%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>快速充電概念領漲+4.05%。其中    笙泉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3122:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3122\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3122-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        聯發科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)            上漲        9.71%            ;        致新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8081-TW</a>)            上漲        5.79%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>矽智財概念領漲+4.03%。其中    智原(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3035:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3035\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3035-TW</a>)            上漲        8.61%            ;        創意(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>)            上漲        7.8%            ;        世芯-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>)            上漲        4.4%    。</p></section></main>",
